## Frontend

- Tamagui +v1.126 for web & native
- Follow Material Design 3 guidelines
- @aipacto/shared-ui-core/*:
  - /components: CoPage, CoText, CoButton, CoCard, CoLink, CoParagraph, CoSpinner, CoTextField, CoToast
  - /icons
  - /theme. Always prioritize custom tokens for colors, spacing, gaps, font sizes, border radius, z-index...
- When adding text for UI add it to common.json and rest of i18n json

## Requirements

- Try to keep comments and docs in the code
- For UI tasks:
  - Use start-end before left-right terms to support ltr/rtl when Tamagui allows it
  - Consider accessibility, follow best practices

